WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:04.150
Hi, my name is Brandon. I've

00:00:04.150 --> 00:00:04.160
had—I

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:06.789
won't call it a visitation, but I saw

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:09.150
some things when I was praying in the

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:12.830
spirit, and I want to tell you

00:00:12.840 --> 00:00:15.470
what the Lord showed me. All right,

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:17.710
here we go. I was praying just like I

00:00:17.720 --> 00:00:20.070
do on a normal night.

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:22.630
It wasn't anything special; there

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:23.790
wasn't anything different about the

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:27.910
prayer. I was just interceding, and it was

00:00:27.910 --> 00:00:27.920
in a Chinese-like

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:31.710
dialect. It

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.470
was different, but it was deep

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:35.630
intercession, so I figured I was praying

00:00:35.640 --> 00:00:39.069
for somebody. In my spirit eyes,

00:00:39.079 --> 00:00:41.549
what the Lord opens up to me whenever

00:00:41.559 --> 00:00:43.510
I'm interceding for somebody, or

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:46.549
the country, or

00:00:46.549 --> 00:00:46.559
whatever—a

00:00:46.559 --> 00:00:48.229
lot of times he'll give me cues and

00:00:48.239 --> 00:00:49.709
show me the direction I'm

00:00:49.719 --> 00:00:52.590
going or who I'm praying for.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:56.069
In this, I started to go into deep

00:00:56.079 --> 00:01:01.349
groanings. It was

00:01:01.359 --> 00:01:03.790
very intense, different than any

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:06.870
other time I've had in a long time.

00:01:06.880 --> 00:01:10.550
Out of my innermost being, out of

00:01:10.560 --> 00:01:12.590
my spirit, it was coming up and rolling

00:01:12.600 --> 00:01:14.390
out of me. In my

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:16.990
intercession, I couldn't get tongues

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.149
out fast enough for what I was

00:01:19.159 --> 00:01:23.710
interceding for. It's like I birthed it,

00:01:23.720 --> 00:01:27.350
and I was translated in my spirit eyes. I

00:01:27.350 --> 00:01:27.360
was

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:31.550
in this jungle-like place, and

00:01:31.550 --> 00:01:31.560
that’s

00:01:31.560 --> 00:01:33.749
all I could see on both

00:01:33.759 --> 00:01:35.990
sides of me, but I was being ushered in. It

00:01:35.990 --> 00:01:36.000
was

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:38.630
like I was being pushed from behind

00:01:38.640 --> 00:01:41.350
very quickly, and all of a

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:44.270
sudden, I saw this temple in front of

00:01:44.280 --> 00:01:47.310
me. I went into this temple that

00:01:47.310 --> 00:01:47.320
was

00:01:47.320 --> 00:01:51.510
like beautiful platinum,

00:01:51.520 --> 00:01:54.469
but it wasn't gold or silver;

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:58.230
it was see-through,

00:01:58.240 --> 00:02:01.069
almost transparent, the most

00:02:01.079 --> 00:02:04.109
beautiful metal.

00:02:04.119 --> 00:02:06.389
I don't know what the throne

00:02:06.389 --> 00:02:06.399
room was;

00:02:06.399 --> 00:02:07.990
I've never seen that on

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.630
this Earth before. I

00:02:10.640 --> 00:02:13.030
went into this temple and

00:02:13.030 --> 00:02:13.040
saw

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:19.390
this being on a throne.

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:21.630
It was carved out

00:02:21.630 --> 00:02:21.640
and

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.990
beautiful. I could see

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.070
the throne, but I could

00:02:26.070 --> 00:02:26.080
only

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:29.470
see a glimpse. I looked up because,

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:29.480
as

00:02:29.480 --> 00:02:31.229
I walked in, he was high and

00:02:31.239 --> 00:02:34.190
lifted up.

00:02:34.200 --> 00:02:36.270
I glimpsed

00:02:36.270 --> 00:02:36.280
and

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:40.190
thought in my

00:02:40.200 --> 00:02:44.710
spirit,

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:48.830
'Where am I? Who is this?'And he said, 'I Am

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:52.550
that I Am.'When he said that, he shook

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:55.869
the whole temple. The

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:58.710
foundation, everything was being shaken by

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:02.509
his words. I screamed; it

00:03:02.519 --> 00:03:04.229
freaked me out because it was so

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:07.949
powerful. At that time, I

00:03:07.959 --> 00:03:11.270
glanced up

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:14.390
to the top and could see this

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:18.110
gold and this red ruby.

00:03:18.120 --> 00:03:20.030
It was

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.229
gorgeous.

00:03:22.239 --> 00:03:25.030
All

00:03:25.040 --> 00:03:27.710
of a sudden, a light

00:03:27.720 --> 00:03:30.429
beyond any kind of light I've ever seen

00:03:30.439 --> 00:03:32.429
appeared.

00:03:32.439 --> 00:03:35.309
There's nothing on this Earth

00:03:35.309 --> 00:03:35.319
as

00:03:35.319 --> 00:03:38.110
bright as what I saw. You can look at the

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:40.990
sun at noon, and it's

00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:43.630
still not as bright.

00:03:43.640 --> 00:03:46.390
There were three stages of light:

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:48.509
a light that wasn't as

00:03:48.519 --> 00:03:50.309
bright, a

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:52.309
brighter light, and then the center light.

00:03:52.319 --> 00:03:54.190
The light in the center was so

00:03:54.200 --> 00:03:56.350
bright it was piercing; if you looked

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.789
at it, it would melt you. I couldn't look

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:00.990
at it. I could see the outer light, but

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:02.710
I tried to glance up

00:04:02.710 --> 00:04:02.720
and

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:04.869
it was

00:04:04.879 --> 00:04:07.589
piercing me. It was

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:09.910
incredible; words cannot

00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.630
describe what I'm trying

00:04:12.640 --> 00:04:15.030
to say. The

00:04:15.040 --> 00:04:17.909
English vocabulary does not wrap

00:04:17.919 --> 00:04:20.390
around my intellect to tell

00:04:20.400 --> 00:04:23.909
you what I was seeing.

00:04:23.919 --> 00:04:26.990
Let me say it like living

00:04:26.990 --> 00:04:27.000
water.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:32.350
When he spoke,

00:04:32.360 --> 00:04:36.550
his words would go out and

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:39.510
stay alive. I can't skip

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:42.310
around too far. Whenever I was at the

00:04:42.320 --> 00:04:46.150
altar, there was water

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:49.390
at the base of it.

00:04:49.390 --> 00:04:49.400
It

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:51.950
was

00:04:51.950 --> 00:04:51.960
ankle-deep,

00:04:51.960 --> 00:04:55.230
knee-deep,

00:04:55.230 --> 00:04:55.240
and

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:57.790
waist-deep,

00:04:57.800 --> 00:04:59.710
and then you could see in the

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:01.909
deep it went over

00:05:01.919 --> 00:05:04.590
an edge and went

00:05:04.600 --> 00:05:07.950
way down. In this water, you

00:05:07.960 --> 00:05:09.909
could take your whole body all the way

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:12.469
to the bottom.

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:16.110
The water was the clearest, bluest,

00:05:16.120 --> 00:05:18.189
most beautiful water I've ever seen.

00:05:18.199 --> 00:05:19.990
You could just drink

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.710
it and want

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:24.029
more because the water was so

00:05:24.039 --> 00:05:26.590
perfect. It was flowing out of the

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:29.710
throne, flowing out of him;

00:05:29.710 --> 00:05:29.720
it

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:32.550
was

00:05:32.560 --> 00:05:36.749
living water.

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:42.870
He spoke to me for about an hour in

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:46.110
this encounter

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:47.870
about the end

00:05:47.880 --> 00:05:50.390
times, the church, and

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:53.870
personal stuff about my life and

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:56.270
family.

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:01.430
When he spoke, his words

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:04.070
would come out of that light

00:06:04.080 --> 00:06:06.469
in

00:06:06.479 --> 00:06:08.070
English, but they would be really

00:06:08.080 --> 00:06:11.629
big, then stop upon the

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:14.309
water and get

00:06:14.319 --> 00:06:16.670
smaller until they

00:06:16.670 --> 00:06:16.680
turned

00:06:16.680 --> 00:06:18.270
into a

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:21.870
seed. The words wouldn't die; they remained alive and

00:06:21.870 --> 00:06:21.880
would start to grow.

00:06:21.880 --> 00:06:24.550
They were like a seed right in front of your face. They started growing and cultivating roots, like a

00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:24.560
potato or a peanut in a farm. The

00:06:24.560 --> 00:06:27.430
words

00:06:27.430 --> 00:06:27.440
became

00:06:27.440 --> 00:06:30.749
alive. Every time he would speak, they would start to

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:44.830
form

00:06:58.550 --> 00:06:58.560
and

00:07:09.560 --> 00:07:14.589
grow together. I know the

00:07:14.599 --> 00:07:18.749
Bible says we are made in his image, but

00:07:22.039 --> 00:07:25.430
he is

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:29.230
God. All of a sudden, out of that light, a

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:32.430
massive eyeball came out.

00:07:32.440 --> 00:07:36.110
It was an all-seeing

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:40.150
eye. It came right up

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:43.230
within probably fifteen feet

00:07:43.230 --> 00:07:43.240
of me.

00:07:43.240 --> 00:07:46.950
It was everything I could do

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:49.710
not to wet myself;

00:07:49.710 --> 00:07:49.720
that’s

00:07:49.720 --> 00:07:51.710
how intense

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:54.430
and

00:07:54.440 --> 00:07:58.110
scary it was. All I wanted to do was cry

00:07:58.120 --> 00:08:00.350
out in repentance and ask God

00:08:00.350 --> 00:08:00.360
to

00:08:00.360 --> 00:08:02.710
forgive me. He

00:08:02.710 --> 00:08:02.720
is

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:06.589
holy and merciful.

00:08:09.080 --> 00:08:12.149
It

00:08:12.159 --> 00:08:14.670
shook me to the core.

00:08:14.680 --> 00:08:18.670
In that eye, in the iris,

00:08:18.680 --> 00:08:22.309
there was fire. The fire was

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:24.790
growing and moving; it

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:27.950
was alive.

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:33.310
The flames were dancing

00:08:33.320 --> 00:08:38.230
upon each other. It was so

00:08:38.240 --> 00:08:41.070
intense.

00:08:41.080 --> 00:08:45.190
Every time he

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:46.470
spoke,

00:08:46.480 --> 00:08:49.430
the words came out

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.870
of that

00:08:51.870 --> 00:08:51.880
light.

00:08:51.880 --> 00:08:54.590
He

00:08:54.590 --> 00:08:54.600
talked

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:57.230
to me about a verse I had

00:08:57.240 --> 00:09:00.550
been discussing with him.

00:09:00.550 --> 00:09:00.560
I’ve

00:09:00.560 --> 00:09:03.110
been hearing from

00:09:03.120 --> 00:09:05.829
certain ministers that

00:09:05.839 --> 00:09:08.470
there is no end-time revival,

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:10.389
but

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:13.069
I was asking

00:09:13.079 --> 00:09:15.310
him about this. I quoted the scripture, 'As

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:17.110
the days of Noah, so will it be when the

00:09:17.120 --> 00:09:19.350
Son of Man returns.'They were put

00:09:19.360 --> 00:09:21.350
in the boat and left; there was

00:09:21.360 --> 00:09:25.389
no big revival.

00:09:25.399 --> 00:09:27.430
I was

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:30.350
praying in tongues, and he was

00:09:30.360 --> 00:09:32.269
speaking to me in

00:09:32.279 --> 00:09:36.790
tongues. His tongue was very deep

00:09:36.790 --> 00:09:36.800
and

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:41.230
masculine,

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:42.990
like

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:45.550
echoes, like living water

00:09:45.560 --> 00:09:47.790
flowing out of him. It was

00:09:47.790 --> 00:09:47.800
a heavenly

00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:51.350
language

00:09:51.350 --> 00:09:51.360
I’ve

00:09:51.360 --> 00:09:53.430
never

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:55.350
heard before.

00:09:58.160 --> 00:10:01.150
His tongue was

00:10:01.160 --> 00:10:03.750
like

00:10:03.750 --> 00:10:03.760
roaring

00:10:03.760 --> 00:10:06.670
thunder when he

00:10:06.670 --> 00:10:06.680
spoke,

00:10:06.680 --> 00:10:09.430
but I understood everything he was

00:10:09.440 --> 00:10:11.829
saying. When I spoke

00:10:11.829 --> 00:10:11.839
in

00:10:11.839 --> 00:10:14.790
tongues, he

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:16.949
understood

00:10:16.949 --> 00:10:16.959
me.

00:10:16.959 --> 00:10:19.829
We were

00:10:19.839 --> 00:10:21.829
talking to each other,

00:10:21.829 --> 00:10:21.839
and

00:10:21.839 --> 00:10:24.310
I understood him in English in my ears even

00:10:24.310 --> 00:10:24.320
though

00:10:24.320 --> 00:10:26.910
it was in

00:10:26.920 --> 00:10:29.150
tongues. He was speaking to me

00:10:31.800 --> 00:10:35.629
as 'I Am that I

00:10:35.629 --> 00:10:35.639
Am.'I

00:10:35.639 --> 00:10:38.550
hope my words are

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:42.509
giving some justice to this.

00:10:42.519 --> 00:10:47.269
He said,

00:10:47.279 --> 00:10:50.230
'Son, you have no idea the real

00:10:50.240 --> 00:10:53.350
translation of those scriptures.

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:55.710
You need to go back to the

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:58.949
Greek and study my word

00:10:58.959 --> 00:11:00.750
more than just the King James or the

00:11:00.760 --> 00:11:03.110
Amplified versions. Study

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:05.190
the meaning of each

00:11:05.190 --> 00:11:05.200
word.'He

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:08.389
asked,

00:11:08.399 --> 00:11:10.990
'Who says that I'm coming back

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:13.990
right now?'I mentioned the signs of the times. He said,

00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.949
'I

00:11:15.959 --> 00:11:19.230
am

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:22.230
in control of

00:11:22.230 --> 00:11:22.240
time,'and

00:11:22.240 --> 00:11:25.389
he shook

00:11:25.399 --> 00:11:28.389
the foundation of the temple.

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:34.030
'I will come back when I am

00:11:34.040 --> 00:11:37.269
ready. I said in my word that I'm

00:11:37.279 --> 00:11:40.509
coming back for a spotless bride, and the

00:11:40.519 --> 00:11:44.710
bride is not ready yet. My Son's

00:11:44.710 --> 00:11:44.720
return—he

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:46.990
doesn't even know, nor the

00:11:47.000 --> 00:11:49.269
angels in heaven. I

00:11:49.279 --> 00:11:52.590
will come back when I am

00:11:52.600 --> 00:11:57.949
ready.'I

00:11:57.959 --> 00:11:59.389
was quoting scriptures

00:11:59.399 --> 00:12:00.949
back to him with my little

00:12:00.959 --> 00:12:02.509
peanut brain,

00:12:02.509 --> 00:12:02.519
but

00:12:02.519 --> 00:12:04.230
he was quoting back a

00:12:04.240 --> 00:12:05.670
thousand more.

00:12:05.680 --> 00:12:07.870
It was just

00:12:07.880 --> 00:12:11.350
flowing out of him.

00:12:11.360 --> 00:12:14.590
He said, 'I want to show

00:12:14.600 --> 00:12:17.230
you something.'I hope I’m not

00:12:17.240 --> 00:12:19.870
skipping around, but the

00:12:19.870 --> 00:12:19.880
Spirit will

00:12:19.880 --> 00:12:21.470
bring stuff back to me.

00:12:21.480 --> 00:12:23.910
There was a preacher—I will

00:12:23.920 --> 00:12:26.269
not release his name—who was

00:12:26.279 --> 00:12:30.230
interceding on the Earth.

00:12:34.079 --> 00:12:35.590
The Lord allowed me to

00:12:35.600 --> 00:12:37.269
hear his prayer. I was standing at

00:12:37.279 --> 00:12:40.150
the altar, and I

00:12:40.150 --> 00:12:40.160
saw a

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:42.710
shaft of light

00:12:42.720 --> 00:12:46.110
like a flaming comet coming up from

00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:49.030
the Earth. It circled the throne room;

00:12:53.440 --> 00:12:55.430
they were prayers echoing

00:12:55.430 --> 00:12:55.440
from

00:12:55.440 --> 00:12:57.230
this

00:12:57.240 --> 00:12:59.750
man. He was interceding

00:12:59.760 --> 00:13:03.150
for the

00:13:03.160 --> 00:13:06.350
continents of the world, and they were

00:13:06.360 --> 00:13:09.470
coming up before the Father.

00:13:09.480 --> 00:13:13.430
This man

00:13:13.440 --> 00:13:16.750
came to the throne room in the spirit,

00:13:16.750 --> 00:13:16.760
and a transparent

00:13:16.760 --> 00:13:20.310
globe wrapped around him.

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:27.750
Beams of light

00:13:27.760 --> 00:13:29.990
were coming out of

00:13:29.990 --> 00:13:30.000
his belly,

00:13:30.000 --> 00:13:32.550
shooting to places on

00:13:32.560 --> 00:13:33.870
the globe

00:13:33.870 --> 00:13:33.880
like

00:13:33.880 --> 00:13:38.870
South America, Europe,

00:13:38.880 --> 00:13:42.189
Asia, America, and Canada.

00:13:42.199 --> 00:13:44.629
He

00:13:44.639 --> 00:13:48.189
was interceding for an

00:13:48.189 --> 00:13:48.199
end-time

00:13:48.199 --> 00:13:51.030
revival. The Lord told me, 'Go and

00:13:51.040 --> 00:13:54.870
tell this family member

00:13:54.870 --> 00:13:54.880
that

00:13:54.880 --> 00:13:58.389
their theology of

00:13:58.399 --> 00:13:59.990
no

00:13:59.990 --> 00:14:00.000
end-time

00:14:00.000 --> 00:14:03.670
revival

00:14:03.680 --> 00:14:08.550
is

00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:12.350
nonsense. There will be a great revival,

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:15.550
a harvest of souls,

00:14:15.560 --> 00:14:18.590
an outpouring of my Spirit, and

00:14:18.600 --> 00:14:20.310
many

00:14:20.320 --> 00:14:25.230
healings. I will not be defeated,

00:14:25.240 --> 00:14:28.829
and you will not be defeated. You will

00:14:28.839 --> 00:14:31.350
walk in a great victory in these last

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:34.310
days. I am not coming back for a

00:14:34.320 --> 00:14:37.790
church that is weak and defeated. You

00:14:37.800 --> 00:14:40.350
will go forth into this world and do

00:14:40.360 --> 00:14:43.069
what I've called you to do

00:14:43.079 --> 00:14:44.670
with great

00:14:44.680 --> 00:14:48.710
victory.'He

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:51.389
said many people

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:57.030
have an escape

00:14:57.040 --> 00:14:59.590
mentality. 'You will not have

00:14:59.590 --> 00:14:59.600
an

00:14:59.600 --> 00:15:02.590
escape mentality because times are

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:05.870
hard. You will press into me and walk in

00:15:05.880 --> 00:15:08.110
my

00:15:08.120 --> 00:15:11.949
glory. I never designed the

00:15:11.959 --> 00:15:15.069
armor for

00:15:15.079 --> 00:15:18.069
retreat;

00:15:18.079 --> 00:15:21.990
I designed it for

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:24.310
charging ahead and taking

00:15:26.670 --> 00:15:26.680
dominion.'He

00:15:30.440 --> 00:15:33.110
said the teaching

00:15:33.110 --> 00:15:33.120
that

00:15:33.120 --> 00:15:35.269
there is no

00:15:35.269 --> 00:15:35.279
end-time revival

00:15:35.279 --> 00:15:37.110
is

00:15:37.120 --> 00:15:39.870
nonsense. When he said that, he was

00:15:39.870 --> 00:15:39.880
angry, and

00:15:39.880 --> 00:15:43.309
it shook the

00:15:43.319 --> 00:15:46.910
foundation. He said there are

00:15:46.920 --> 00:15:50.389
challenging times

00:15:50.399 --> 00:15:59.430
ahead. There's a great

00:15:59.440 --> 00:16:03.590
shifting—like

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:07.069
corn being shucked. He said,

00:16:07.079 --> 00:16:09.749
'I'm going to shuck the corn,

00:16:09.749 --> 00:16:09.759
son.'I'm

00:16:09.759 --> 00:16:11.550
from Oklahoma,

00:16:11.550 --> 00:16:11.560
so

00:16:11.560 --> 00:16:13.509
I get that. 'We're going to

00:16:13.519 --> 00:16:15.470
pull it back,

00:16:15.480 --> 00:16:18.030
clean it up, and

00:16:18.040 --> 00:16:20.509
make it

00:16:20.519 --> 00:16:24.590
ready.'He

00:16:24.600 --> 00:16:26.470
showed me the

00:16:26.480 --> 00:16:28.509
bride

00:16:28.519 --> 00:16:30.350
in the throne room.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:34.350
She had a beautiful lace gown,

00:16:36.519 --> 00:16:39.590
but

00:16:41.550 --> 00:16:41.560
it

00:16:43.680 --> 00:16:46.150
had black

00:16:46.160 --> 00:16:49.350
spots

00:16:49.350 --> 00:16:49.360
and

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:53.550
smudges like

00:16:53.560 --> 00:16:55.670
soot.

00:16:55.680 --> 00:16:58.949
He said, 'I told

00:16:58.959 --> 00:17:01.030
you in my word that I'm coming back for

00:17:01.040 --> 00:17:04.990
a spotless bride. It's time for you to

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:08.110
come out of the ankle-deep water and come to the deeper water.'I wanted to go in that deep water

00:17:12.439 --> 00:17:15.630
so bad.

00:17:30.520 --> 00:17:33.470
He

00:17:33.480 --> 00:17:35.270
said, 'Brandon, you've been in that deeper

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:39.190
water before. It's like muscle

00:17:39.200 --> 00:17:42.150
memory. You'll

00:17:49.679 --> 00:17:51.430
build your muscles up

00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:53.190
spiritually and

00:17:53.200 --> 00:17:55.789
just flow back into it.

00:17:55.789 --> 00:17:55.799
Seek

00:17:55.799 --> 00:17:56.830
me.'He

00:17:56.830 --> 00:17:56.840
talked

00:17:59.870 --> 00:17:59.880
to

00:17:59.880 --> 00:18:02.430
me

00:18:02.430 --> 00:18:02.440
about

00:18:02.440 --> 00:18:04.590
finances

00:18:04.600 --> 00:18:06.750
because I’ve been praying

00:18:10.360 --> 00:18:13.350
for

00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:18.440
million-dollar

00:18:22.110 --> 00:18:22.120
ideas.

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.750
He said sternly, 'Where in my

00:18:27.760 --> 00:18:30.990
word did I

00:18:31.000 --> 00:18:33.230
tell you to pray like that?

00:18:36.120 --> 00:18:38.430
Seek first the

00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:41.029
kingdom, and all these things will be

00:18:41.039 --> 00:18:45.110
added unto you. Seeking

00:18:45.120 --> 00:18:48.149
finances that way is idolatry.

00:18:48.159 --> 00:18:51.630
Seek me,

00:18:51.640 --> 00:18:54.590
and I will give you the

00:18:54.600 --> 00:18:59.310
secret things.

00:18:59.320 --> 00:19:02.669
I have no problem blessing

00:19:02.669 --> 00:19:02.679
you with

00:19:02.679 --> 00:19:05.430
money

00:19:05.440 --> 00:19:07.789
as long as that money doesn't

00:19:07.799 --> 00:19:11.029
have you. As soon as

00:19:11.039 --> 00:19:12.909
I can trust you with that

00:19:12.919 --> 00:19:15.590
outflow, you'll have

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:18.110
it.'I

00:19:18.120 --> 00:19:20.270
told

00:19:20.280 --> 00:19:21.390
him

00:19:21.400 --> 00:19:23.470
I

00:19:23.480 --> 00:19:27.630
was

00:19:27.640 --> 00:19:29.870
sorry and

00:19:29.870 --> 00:19:29.880
that

00:19:29.880 --> 00:19:34.350
I

00:19:34.350 --> 00:19:34.360
wanted

00:19:34.360 --> 00:19:36.470
to be

00:19:36.480 --> 00:19:38.830
spotless

00:19:38.830 --> 00:19:38.840
and

00:19:38.840 --> 00:19:42.110
usable.

00:19:42.120 --> 00:19:45.909
Jesus is

00:19:45.919 --> 00:19:48.190
coming back for a

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:50.149
victorious church, not

00:19:50.149 --> 00:19:50.159
one

00:19:50.159 --> 00:19:52.470
that

00:19:52.470 --> 00:19:52.480
is

00:19:52.480 --> 00:19:56.110
retreating. The gospel that

00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:59.110
must be preached is repentance.

00:19:59.110 --> 00:19:59.120
We

00:19:59.120 --> 00:20:02.789
must

00:20:02.799 --> 00:20:06.789
seek his face and

00:20:18.159 --> 00:20:21.070
know his

00:20:21.080 --> 00:20:24.190
heart. He said, 'If you lay your head upon

00:20:24.200 --> 00:20:29.190
my chest every day, I will

00:20:29.190 --> 00:20:29.200
whisper

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:31.029
the secret

00:20:31.039 --> 00:20:35.029
things

00:20:35.039 --> 00:20:37.590
to

00:20:37.600 --> 00:20:42.870
you

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:46.310
in

00:20:46.320 --> 00:20:49.430
a

00:20:49.440 --> 00:20:54.390
still, small

00:20:54.390 --> 00:20:54.400
voice.'I

00:20:54.400 --> 00:21:02.870
was interceding for America

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:06.669
and crying out for

00:21:06.679 --> 00:21:08.669
revival

00:21:14.159 --> 00:21:17.549
on the East

00:21:17.559 --> 00:21:21.390
Coast. He told me, 'I will not let

00:21:21.400 --> 00:21:25.350
America become a goat

00:21:25.360 --> 00:21:30.630
nation, for your founding fathers

00:21:30.640 --> 00:21:32.710
made a covenant with

00:21:32.720 --> 00:21:37.110
me.'He

00:21:37.120 --> 00:21:39.870
took me to Plymouth Rock

00:21:39.880 --> 00:21:43.549
and showed me the pilgrims

00:21:43.549 --> 00:21:43.559
making

00:21:43.559 --> 00:21:46.909
a covenant

00:21:50.880 --> 00:21:52.950
and

00:21:57.960 --> 00:21:59.950
taking

00:21:59.960 --> 00:22:02.430
communion.

00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:04.909
He said

00:22:04.919 --> 00:22:09.269
those prayers still echo

00:22:09.279 --> 00:22:12.990
in

00:22:13.000 --> 00:22:13.870
his

00:22:13.880 --> 00:22:18.350
ears.

00:22:21.279 --> 00:22:24.190
I saw George Washington

00:22:24.200 --> 00:22:26.830
crying out on the battlefield,

00:22:37.760 --> 00:22:41.190
and God gave him

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:44.149
strength

00:22:44.159 --> 00:22:48.310
and

00:22:48.320 --> 00:22:51.630
victory.

00:22:53.320 --> 00:22:56.149
The Lord said those men

00:22:56.159 --> 00:22:58.830
died for

00:23:00.080 --> 00:23:02.630
freedom, and he will not let

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:06.029
their blood go. He said

00:23:08.200 --> 00:23:10.710
what we are going

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:14.430
through

00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:18.390
now

00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:20.549
is not

00:23:20.559 --> 00:23:25.149
judgment,

00:23:36.360 --> 00:23:39.269
but correction. 'True

00:23:39.279 --> 00:23:42.870
judgment is separation from me

00:23:42.870 --> 00:23:42.880
for

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:45.750
eternity.

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:48.470
This

00:23:48.480 --> 00:23:50.430
is

00:23:50.440 --> 00:23:52.190
just

00:23:52.200 --> 00:23:54.070
correction.

00:23:59.279 --> 00:24:01.630
You will be

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:04.269
a sheep nation.'He said things

00:24:04.269 --> 00:24:04.279
are

00:24:04.279 --> 00:24:08.430
coming to this area

00:24:08.430 --> 00:24:08.440
and

00:24:08.440 --> 00:24:14.789
we

00:24:14.789 --> 00:24:14.799
must

00:24:14.799 --> 00:24:18.070
draw close

00:24:18.080 --> 00:24:21.070
to him

00:24:21.080 --> 00:24:23.149
to hear

00:24:23.159 --> 00:24:27.149
what's coming. There's a

00:24:27.149 --> 00:24:27.159
shaking

00:24:27.159 --> 00:24:29.710
coming,

00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:33.310
but

00:24:33.320 --> 00:24:36.870
it's a

00:24:36.870 --> 00:24:36.880
father's

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:39.710
love. A great revival

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:42.669
is coming, and no man will get the glory. I

00:24:42.679 --> 00:24:46.990
saw

00:24:59.240 --> 00:25:03.269
glory domes

00:25:03.269 --> 00:25:03.279
where

00:25:03.279 --> 00:25:06.630
people

00:25:06.640 --> 00:25:09.549
were

00:25:09.559 --> 00:25:12.110
healed by the

00:25:12.120 --> 00:25:15.389
power of God. People

00:25:20.559 --> 00:25:22.110
were coming

00:25:22.120 --> 00:25:25.190
from everywhere to be part of

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:27.909
it.

00:25:27.919 --> 00:25:30.310
There was revival happening everywhere,

00:25:30.320 --> 00:25:32.669
but especially in the center of America.

00:25:37.559 --> 00:25:39.909
Lives were being changed

00:25:39.919 --> 00:25:41.430
throughout the

00:25:43.510 --> 00:25:43.520
world—Europe,

00:25:47.000 --> 00:25:49.830
Africa,

00:25:49.840 --> 00:25:52.590
everywhere.

00:25:52.590 --> 00:25:52.600
I

00:25:52.600 --> 00:25:53.990
want to thank you all for

00:25:54.000 --> 00:25:56.830
listening.

00:25:56.840 --> 00:25:59.750
I pray, Father,

00:25:59.760 --> 00:26:02.789
in the name of Jesus,

00:26:05.440 --> 00:26:07.590
that you anoint these people

00:26:07.600 --> 00:26:10.190
to do something great.

00:26:10.200 --> 00:26:13.669
Pour out your Spirit.

00:26:13.679 --> 00:26:16.110
We are the

00:26:16.120 --> 00:26:19.029
head and not the tail.

00:26:22.799 --> 00:26:25.350
I take authority over

00:26:25.360 --> 00:26:28.389
sickness and disease right now.

00:26:30.559 --> 00:26:33.789
Satan,

00:26:33.799 --> 00:26:36.710
leave them alone. I call them healed

00:26:36.720 --> 00:26:38.750
and whole by the power of the

00:26:38.760 --> 00:26:41.710
blood of Jesus, from the

00:26:41.710 --> 00:26:41.720
top of

00:26:41.720 --> 00:26:44.430
their heads

00:26:44.430 --> 00:26:44.440
to

00:26:44.440 --> 00:26:46.510
the

00:26:46.510 --> 00:26:46.520
soles

00:26:46.520 --> 00:26:49.190
of their feet. Thank you for

00:26:49.200 --> 00:26:50.789
the blood and

00:26:50.789 --> 00:26:50.799
for forgiving

00:26:50.799 --> 00:26:52.549
our sins.

00:26:54.480 --> 00:26:56.870
I give you praise

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:59.110
and glory for what you're about to do. In

00:27:02.039 --> 00:27:04.669
Jesus'name,

00:27:06.440 --> 00:27:09.669
have a blessed

00:27:09.679 --> 00:27:12.789
day,

00:27:12.789 --> 00:27:12.799
and

00:27:12.799 --> 00:27:15.110
I appreciate you

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:19.039
listening. Bye-bye.

